- This should be good.

395
00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:31.480
I didn't get
my Christmas bonus.

396
00:20:31.600 --> 00:20:34.160
I tried not to let it
ruin Christmas for eveybody.

397
00:20:34.280 --> 00:20:36.080
but no matter
what I did--

398
00:20:36.200 --> 00:20:39.560
- Hey. eveybody. lookwhat we got!

399
00:20:39.560 --> 00:20:42.320
A dog!
All right. Dad!

400
00:20:42.440 --> 00:20:46.160
- God bless him.
- So love at first sight is possible.

401
00:20:46.280 --> 00:20:48.760
And if he runs away.
he'll be easy to catch.

402
00:20:48.760 --> 00:20:50.880
Oh.
this is the best gift of all. Homer!

403
00:20:50.960 --> 00:20:53.560
- It is? -
Yes. Something to share our love...

404
00:20:53.560 --> 00:20:55.480
and frighten prowlers.

405
00:20:55.480 --> 00:20:57.680
- What's his name?
- Number 8--

406
00:20:57.680 --> 00:21:00.360
I mean. Santa's Little Helper.

407
00:21:13.400 --> 00:21:16.000
Rudolph the red-nosed
reindeer

408
00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:19.080
Had a very shiny nose

409
00:21:19.160 --> 00:21:21.840
And if you ever saw it

410
00:21:21.960 --> 00:21:24.920
- you would even say it glows
- Like a light bulb!

411
00:21:24.920 --> 00:21:27.800
-Bart!
- All of the other reindeer

412
00:21:27.800 --> 00:21:29.720
Used to laugh
and call him names

413
00:21:29.720 --> 00:21:31.640
- Like Shnozzola!
-Lisa!

414
00:21:31.640 --> 00:21:33.840
They never let poor Rudolph

415
00:21:33.920 --> 00:21:36.600
- Join in any reindeergames
-Like strippoker!

416
00:21:36.720 --> 00:21:39.960
-I'm warning you two!
- Then one foggy Christmas Eve

417
00:21:40.080 --> 00:21:42.960
- Santa came to say
- Take it. Homer!

418
00:21:42.960 --> 00:21:46.320
Uh. Rudolph get your nose over here

419
00:21:46.400 --> 00:21:49.760
- So you can guide my sleigh today
- Oh. Homer.

420
00:21:49.760 --> 00:21:52.520
Then all the reindeer
loved him

421
00:21:52.520 --> 00:21:55.520
and they shouted out
with glee

422
00:21:55.600 --> 00:21:58.280
Rudolph the red-nosed
reindeer

423
00:21:58.400 --> 00:22:01.840
You'll go down in history

424
00:22:01.840 --> 00:22:03.360
-Like Attila the Hu--
- You little--

425
00:22:06.920 --> 00:22:08.760
Shh.
